data.description: Nestled in the sought-after Sunrise Ridge community in Martinez, this 3 bedroom 2 bathroom townhome offers a spacious interior, numerous amenities, and convenient location, with easy access to I-680 and HWY 4.  The upstairs main living area features an open concept with vaulted ceilings that seamlessly connect the living room, dining area, and kitchen. Leading to the peaceful front balcony deck. Great for entertaining guests or spending quality time with loved ones. The refreshed kitchen has newer granite counter tops, the bathrooms have new counters as well, and fresh interior & exterior paint throughout the whole townhome.  With the primary bed and bath upstairs, the lower level sports two more bedrooms with another bathroom, convenient laundry closet, and leads to the private backyard patio w/ a gate to the walking path, and no rear neighbors. A two-car attached garage offers secure parking and additional storage options. Residents of Sunrise Ridge enjoy access to the community pool, greenbelt, playground, and tennis/pickle ball courts All for an affordable HOA Fee of $165/month. Don't miss this one!
